    <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">place</rdfs:label>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="en">A location.

The entity defined as place encompasses a comprehensive range of locations: terrestrial and extra-terrestrial; historical and contemporary; geographic features and geo-political jurisdictions. </rdfs:comment>
