    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="en">A manifestation that embodies an expression.</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="en">As defined by FRBR (http://www.ifla.org/VII/s13/frbr/frbr1.htm; http://purl.org/vocab/frbr/core#embodimentOf), a property representing an expression that is embodied by a manifestation.</rdfs:comment>
